  "output": "## Performance Analysis Report\n\nHere are the real issues found across 8 files, ordered by severity:\n\n---\n\n### 1. N+1 / Repeated Async Calls\n\n**`src/core/HistoryOfThought.js`** вҖ” `openDB()` called on every `appendEvent()` invocation instead of reusing a persistent connection:\n```js\n// Fix: singleton connection\nlet dbConnection = null;\nasync function getDB() {\n  if (!dbConnection) dbConnection = await openDB();\n  return dbConnection;\n}\n```\n\n**`src/frontend/UniversalOnboarding.js`** вҖ” `processDocumentWithGCP` called sequentially in a `for...of` loop. Parallelise:\n```js\n// Before: sequential await in loop\n// After:\nconst results = await Promise.all(files.map(f => processDocumentWithGCP(f)));\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. Unnecessary Re-renders\n\n**`src/frontend/SettingsContext.js`** вҖ” Monolithic `useEffect` with 20+ dependencies writes all localStorage keys on any single setting change. Split into one effect per key. Also, the context value object is created inline on every render вҖ” wrap it in `useMemo`.\n\n**`src/frontend/LinearCanvas.js`** вҖ” `ToneHUD` runs regex splits and `Set` construction on every render:\n```js\n// Wrap in useMemo keyed to currentContent\nconst metrics = useMemo(() => {\n  const wordCount = currentContent.split(/\\s+/).filter(Boolean).length;\n  const longWords = (currentContent.match(/\\b\\w{8,}\\b/g) || []).length;\n  return { wordCount, rigor: (longWords / wordCount * 100).toFixed(1) };\n}, [currentContent]);\n```\n\n**`src/frontend/ProjectContext.js`** вҖ” `__overriddenExtractionData` and `__overriddenRoadmap` are computed as IIFEs inside render. Wrap both in `useMemo([__schemaPillars])`.\n\n---\n\n### 3. Caching Opportunities\n\n**`src/services/BriefService.js`** вҖ” 15+ regex literals compiled on every function call. Hoist them to module scope:\n```js\n// Module-level constants (compiled once):\nconst THEME_REGEX = /\\b[\\w\\s&]+\\b/g;\nconst LEARNING_OUTCOME_REGEX = /(?:Learning Outcomes?|LOs?|Course Goals?)/gi;\n// ... etc.\n```\n\n**`src/core/HistoryOfThought.js`** вҖ” `deviceSignature()` async function recomputed on every `appendEvent`. Cache after first call:\n```js\nlet _sig = null;\nasync function deviceSignature() {\n  if (!_sig) _sig = await computeSignature();\n  return _sig;\n}\n```\n\n**`src/core/ExecutiveSpine.js`** вҖ” Repeated `localStorage.getItem()` calls without in-memory cache. Add a simple keyвҶ’value map with invalidation on `setItem`.\n\n---\n\n### 4. Memory Leaks\n\n**`src/frontend/MasterDashboard.js`** вҖ” Multiple `window.addEventListener` calls in `useEffect` with no cleanup:\n```js\nuseEffect(() => {\n  window.addEventListener('toggle-view-mode', handler);\n  return () => window.removeEventListener('toggle-view-mode', handler);\n}, []);\n```\n\n**`src/core/ExecutiveSpine.js`** вҖ” `setInterval` for idle detection starts a new interval on every call without clearing the previous one. Guard with a module-level variable:\n```js\nlet idleInterval = null;\nfunction startIdleDetection() {\n  if (idleInterval) return;\n  idleInterval = setInterval(checkIdle, 15_000);\n}\nfunction stopIdleDetection() {\n  clearInterval(idleInterval);\n  idleInterval = null;\n}\n```\n\nNested `setTimeout` in `grantPlayTime` also leaks on repeated calls вҖ” store both timer IDs and clear before re-setting.\n\n---\n\n### 5. Redundant Computations\n\n**`src/frontend/LinearCanvas.js`** (`SectionHealth`) вҖ” word count and percentage recomputed every render. Wrap in `React.memo` + `useMemo`:\n```js\nconst SectionHealth = React.memo(({ content, maxWords }) => {\n  const { wordCount, pct } = useMemo(() => ({\n    wordCount: content.split(/\\s+/).length,\n    pct: (content.split(/\\s+/).length / maxWords * 100).toFixed(1)\n  }), [content, maxWords]);\n  return <div>{pct}%</div>;\n});\n```\n\nHistory scrubbing (`historyWords.map(...)`) runs on every slider movement вҖ” memoize the rendered spans with `useMemo([isScrubbing, historyWords])`.\n\n**`src/frontend/MasterDashboard.js`** вҖ” `synthesiseMilestones` called inside a `tasks.map()` without memoization. Wrap the entire map in `useMemo([tasks])`.\n\n---\n\n### Priority Order\n\n| # | File | Fix | Impact |\n|---|------|-----|--------|\n| 1 | `SettingsContext.js` | Split useEffect + memoize value | Eliminates cascade re-renders on every setting |\n| 2 | `LinearCanvas.js` | `useMemo` on ToneHUD + SectionHealth | Stops regex on every keystroke |\n| 3 | `BriefService.js` | Hoist regex to module scope | Compile cost amortised across lifetime |\n| 4 | `HistoryOfThought.js` | Singleton DB + cache deviceSignature | Eliminates repeated IndexedDB opens |\n| 5 | `ExecutiveSpine.js` | Guard interval + clear timers | Prevents timer accumulation leaks |\n| 6 | `MasterDashboard.js` | Add cleanup returns to useEffect | Prevents listener accumulation |\n",
